{"tid":1450513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:05:44.000Z","uid":276614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a67cf673adc1bc8f863f6d78edcb9f5908892e2","tid":1450513,"uid":276614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:20.000Z","msg":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=d2c109e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvm7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=09fae4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"ef675ef151116b3cfc54779fe153d42e64834510","tid":1450513,"uid":276614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:35.000Z","msg":"721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5a0ba19cf65f1f4eeeba252df040606f3cc8da","tid":1450513,"uid":9824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:41:06.000Z","msg":"推晒上熱門"},{"pid":"3dc4572f5b854de2505439286688778f2a0f4c71","tid":1450513,"uid":78333,"like":0,"dislike":0